summary: This new file, moviepage13.html, introduces a webpage dedicated to a specific movie, "Spider-Man: Into The Spider-Verse". The file includes the movie poster, a summary of the movie, a video trailer, and a rating system where users can provide feedback on the movie. The file also includes a navigation menu and a home button for easy navigation within the system. This file contributes to the system by providing a detailed view of a particular movie and allowing user interaction through the rating system. It enhances the user experience by adding more content and functionality to the system.
